Careers








We are a customer-centric company driven by modern technology with one industry focus – insurance, and one core principle – to deliver the best to our customers and add value to their business.

Our world class products and services cater to insurance carriers across the globe, ranging from startups to leading organizations. We understand that the best solutions come from the best people, and the best people are built in the best environments. We therefore nurture a culture of deep knowledge, growth, and learning.

Contact us at:  careers@majesco.com



  
