About Majesco Entertainment





 Our BusinessWe are an innovative provider of interactive entertainment and video games for core gamers and casual gamers alike. We focus on developing and publishing a wide range of casual and core oriented titles on leading console and portable systems. Our diverse product portfolio provides us with multiple opportunities to capitalize on the large and growing installed base of digital entertainment platforms and an increasing number of digital entertainment enthusiasts. Over our 25 year history we have developed strong retail and distribution network relationships that enable us to sell our products to U.S. retail chains, including WalMart, GameStop, Best Buy, Target and Toys 'R Us. We publish our games digitally on Steam, XBLA, PSN, Nintendo, IOS and Android platforms. We publish titles under the name Majesco Entertainment and Midnight City Games. Corporate InformationMajesco Entertainment Company was incorporated in 1986 under the laws of the State of New Jersey. On December 5, 2003,  Majesco Sales Inc. became a wholly-owned subsidiary and the sole operating business of the public company. On April 11, 2005, the public company changed its name to ‘‘Majesco Entertainment Company'' to better reflect its current operating business and Joined the NASDAQ listing. It has since become a privately owned and run company.  Our principal executive offices are located at 82 Bethany Road, Suite4 Hazlet NJ 07730, and our telephone number is (732) 476-1969.  


















